        "valueString": "During the hospital course, the patient was closely monitored for his condition. A multidisciplinary approach was used to optimize the patient's care. In order to maintain the patient's hemodynamic status, ECMO support was initiated. The patient was then closely monitored in the intensive care unit for improvement."
